<body>
<div type="description" n="monument">
<head>Description of Monument</head>
<p><rs type="material">White marble</rs> <rs type="objectType">block</rs> chipped along the upper edge and still partly buried (visible <measure dim="width" type="length" unit="metre">1.13</measure> x<measure dim="height" type="length" unit="metre"> 0.38</measure> x <measure dim="width" type="length" unit="metre">0.62</measure>).</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="text">
<head>Description of Text</head>
<p><rs type="execution" key="scalpro">Inscribed</rs> on the face.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="letters">
<head>Letters</head>
<p>Early, probably I A.D.; ave. <measure dim="height" type="length" unit="metre">0.018</measure>. pi with a short second upright; rho with a small stroke from the lower junction of the bowll with the upright; serifs small and not invariably used; lineation uneven.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="date">
<head>Date</head>
<p><date notBefore="0001" notAfter="0100" exact="none">First century A.D.</date> (<rs type="criteria">lettering</rs>).</p>
 </div>
<div type="edition" lang="grc">
<head lang="en">Edition</head>
<ab><lb n="1"/> <w lemma="ὁ">ὁ</w> <w lemma="δῆμος">δῆμος</w> <w lemma="θάπτω">ἔθαψε<unclear reason="damage">ν</unclear></w> <persName type="aphrodisian"><name reg="Ἄτταλος"><supplied reason="lost">Ἄτ</supplied><lb n="2" type="worddiv"/>ταλον</name> <persName type="aphrodisian"><name reg="Ἄτταλος">Ἀττάλου</name> <supplied reason="lost">τοῦ</supplied>  <lb n="3"/> <persName type="aphrodisian"><name reg="Ἄτταλος">Ἀττάλου</name> <w lemma="ὁ">τοῦ</w> <persName type="aphrodisian"><name reg="Ἑρμόλαος">Ἑρμολά<lb n="4" type="worddiv"/>ου</name></persName></persName></persName></persName> <w lemma="παῖς">παῖδα</w> <w lemma="ὁ">τὴν</w> <w lemma="ἡλικία">ἡλικίαν</w> <lb n="5"/> <w lemma="καί">καὶ</w> <w lemma="στεφανόω">ἐστεφάνωσεν</w> <w lemma="χρυσός">χρυ<lb n="6" type="worddiv"/>σῷ</w> <w lemma="στέφανος">στεφάνωι</w> <space extent="3" unit="character" dim="horizontal"/>  <lb n="6a"/>  <space extent="3" unit="character" dim="horizontal"/>  </ab>
</div>
<div type="translation">
<head>Translation</head>
<p>The People buried Attalos son of Attalos son of Attalos son of Hermolaos, a boy in age-group, and crowned him with a gold crown.</p>
</div>
<div type="commentary">
<head>Commentary</head>
<p>The honorand was from a family of the civic aristocracy. The text also attests a formal organisation of children, and the civic practice of honours  for the children of the prominent</p>
</div>
